multiflexi-microsoft365 (0.1.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Initial release: Office 365 / SharePoint credential prototype split out of
    php-vitexsoftware-multiflexi-core into its own add-on package.
  * Two binary packages: multiflexi-microsoft365 (core) and
    multiflexi-microsoft365-ui (web interface).
  * checkAvailability(): two-phase connection check (acquire token, then a real
    SharePoint REST call) built on vgrem/php-spo; prefers Entra ID v2
    client_credentials with legacy ACS fallback; distinguishes transient from
    permanent failures and never logs the client secret.
  * postinst runs multiflexi-cli credential-prototype:sync.

 -- Vitex <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Mon, 06 Jul 2026 08:00:00 +0200
